Partisan Ranking of Massachusetts Municipalities

Rankings

This map is a cartogram showing partisan rankings of Massachusetts municipalities. Municipalities are sized by 2010 population.

Row

Partisan ranking, by population

About

Rankings are computed as the average difference between Democratic and Republican vote percentages for statewide elections from 2006 to 2012. See How Democratic or Republican is my town? for details of the methodology and source for the data.

The map is a cartogram - the sizes and shapes of municipalities are distorted to reflect the 2010 population.

Mapping by Kent S Johnson.
